705214f-b.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - Dahill Road
705214f-b.text:
(1)
447 King's Highway, at the N.W. corner of Dahill road, showing the C. Stillwell house in 1860.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, showing a front view.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same; looking east, showing also the Culver Line of the B.M.T. on McDonald Ave.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
